extDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Zusammenfassung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Gibt an, ob ein Event in der DOM-Hierarchie nach oben propagiert wird&nbsp;oder nicht.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax_2","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">event.bubbles</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"wert","title":"Wert","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Ein <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, welches <code>true</code>&nbsp;ist, falls das Event durch die DOM-Hierarchie nach oben propagiert wird.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">goInput</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// checks bubbles and</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bubbles<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n     <span class=\"token comment\">// passes event along if it's not</span>\n     <span class=\"token function\">passItOn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// already bubbling</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">doOutput</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Hinweis</strong>: Nur bestimmte Events können weiter nach oben propagiert werden. Die Events, die dazu in der Lage sind, haben den Wert <em>true, &nbsp;</em>für die hier beschriebene Eigenschaft.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://dom.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-event-bubbles\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">DOM<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Event.bubbles' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Events/events.html#Events-Event-canBubble\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Events Specification<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Event.bubbles' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Veraltet</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Zusammenfassung","id":"summary"},{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax_2"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"}],"summary":"Gibt an, ob ein Event in der DOM-Hierarchie nach oben propagiert wird oder nicht.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Event.bubbles","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"event.bubbles","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Event.bubbles","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Event.bubbles","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Event.bubbles","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"event.bubbles","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Event.bubbles","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"event.bubbles","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Event.bubbles","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/event/bubbles","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/event/bubbles/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Event","title":"Event"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Event/bubbles","title":"Event.bubbles"}],"pageTitle":"Event.bubbles - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}